AND DbT1001Hiho."shikakuHenkoYMD" IS NOT NULL AND DbT1001Hiho."shikakuShutokuYMD" = #{shikakuShutokuYMD} AND DbT1001Hiho."logicalDeletedFlag"<> true ORDER BY DbT1001Hiho."idoYMD" desc
